Thank you for providing more examples of Midjourney prompts. These examples further demonstrate the level of detail and specificity that can be used in text prompts to generate desired images. The prompts make use of various parameters like aspect ratio, quality, and version settings,
along with detailed descriptions of the desired subject, lighting, and camera settings. These examples will be useful for understanding the range of possibilities when generating images using Midjourney
